article_id:639,category_name:News,title_name:Issue Regarding Afflictions[Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We have confirmed an issue in version 1.10.0 where certain afflictions do not take effect properly despite the visual effects of the affliction appearing.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently investigating this issue.</div><div>Any updates will be added to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564404300"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>As a temporary measure, we will be reverting the affliction mechanic back to that of 1.9.1 in the next data update scheduled to take place at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564462800"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>Also, changes to afflictions will be postponed to a later update in order to fix this issue in version 1.10.0.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564478400"></span>]</strong></span></div><div>We have reverted the affliction mechanic back to that of version 1.9.1 in the data update applied at <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1564462800"></span> before the automatic update.</div><div><br></div><div>We will announce the agenda for the affliction mechanic changes that were originally planned in version 1.10.0 in a separate notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(44, 130, 201);"><strong>[Addendum <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567058400"></span>]<br></strong></span>The changes to how afflictions work, which were scheduled for release in version 1.10.0, were applied in an automatic update performed around <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1567047600"></span>.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1564387200,update_time1567058560